<span style="font-weight: bold;"><br>
The back story: </span>I have a special place in my heart for games
with no commercial
potential (all you need is a checkerboard and a few extra
checkers).&nbsp; I discovered Tumblingdown while researching stacking
games - it was the runner-up of a game design contest and seemed worthy
of more exposure.&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>
